These are the options that our app should have:

Preferred actions:
Preferred Action when Upgrading *done, we should not do the same when processing queue as it could be dangerous if somebody made a mistake*
Reduce To tray when queue is started and process in tray

Action when app is sitting in the tray
Update database every x
Look for upgrades every x

Application preferences:
Start in the Tray


